text: The William G. and Anne Williams House is a historic building in Sparta, Wisconsin that is now a four-room bed and breakfast. The Williams house is a Queen Anne style Victorian home that has been on the Wisconsin State and National Register of Historic Places since 2005.http://www.wisconsinhistory.org/hp/register/nrviewfull.asphttp://nrhp.focus.nps.gov/natregsearchresult.do?fullresult=true&recordid;=5 The home is known officially on the historical register as the Williams, William G. and Anne, House. The home was built by, W. G.
